enableContextMenu();

var speed = 20; //"speed" of the animation
var strokes = saveData.split(";");
var currStroke = 0;
var currPt = 4;
var img = createGraphics(400, 400, P2D);
img.background(255);

function drawSketch(saveData) {
    
    for (var i = 0; i < speed; i++) {
        
        var pts;
        var curr = strokes[currStroke].split(',');
        if (curr.length === 2) {
            pts = curr[1];
            var settings = curr[0];
            if (settings.length === 2) {
                img.strokeWeight(parseInt(settings, 18));
            } else if (settings.length === 8) {
                var clr = parseInt(settings, 16);
                img.stroke((clr & 255) << 24 | clr >>> 8);
            } else {
                img.strokeWeight(parseInt(settings.slice(0, 2), 18));
                var clr = parseInt(settings.slice(2, 10), 16);
                img.stroke((clr & 255) << 24 | clr >>> 8);
            }
        } else {
            pts = curr[0];
        }
        if (pts[currPt]) {
            var p1 = parseInt(pts.slice(currPt - 4, currPt), 36);
            var p2 = parseInt(pts.slice(currPt, currPt + 4), 36);
            img.line(p1 % img.width, p1 / img.width, p2 % img.width, p2 / img.width);
            currPt += 4;
        } else {
            currPt = 4;
            currStroke++;
            if (!strokes[currStroke]) {
                noLoop();
                return;
            }
            break;
        }
        image(img, 0, 0, width, height);
    }
}

var draw = function() {
    drawSketch();
};
